              <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Every <fr:link href="/jms-00KS/" title="Section-retraction pair" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KS/" display-uri="jms-00KS" type="local">section</fr:link> is <fr:link href="/jms-00MO/" title="Injection" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00MO/" display-uri="jms-00MO" type="local">injective</fr:link></html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>30</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="/jms-00KS/" title="Section-retraction pair" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KS/" display-uri="jms-00KS" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1,b_2\in  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}=s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1=b_2]]></fr:tex>. We have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> by assumption, and thus <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=b_2]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
